A '''blowmolding machine''' is widely used in commercial beverage production. A blowmolding machine creates a [[plastic bottle]] according to a recipe, for example specifying the capacity of the bottle to be made. The machine consists of molds, a [[programmable logic controller]], and mechanical and electronic instruments.

For more information about the process, refer to [[Blow molding]].

